sentences: Ummet Ozcan (Turkish: Ümmet Özcan, IPA: [ymˈmet øzˈdʒan]; born 16 August 1982) is a Dutch DJ and record producer of Turkish heritage from Putten, Gelderland.
In late 2012, he started performing big room house alongside Dimitri Vegas & Like Mike and R3hab for release on the main Spinnin label.

In his early years, Ozcan produced techno-influenced trance music for release under Reset Records.
After nearly five years, Ummet's production shifted focus towards the electronic dance music movement.
In recent years he dedicated himself to other sub-genres and gradually quitted big room house.
HYO) "The Hum", "Melody", "Wake Up The Sun", "Everything Changes" and "Higher".
